A new sharpshooter genus for Sphinctogonia lingula Yang &amp; Li (Hemiptera, Cicadellidae, Cicadellini) from ChinaA new genus, Sphinctogoniella, is described to accommodate Sphinctogonia lingula Yang & Li, 2002, its type species from China. Sphinctogoniella lingula (Yang & Li, 2002), comb. n. is re-described and illustrated. Differences between the new genus and Sphinctogonia Breddin, 1901 are tabulated.